    "en": {
      "name": "Maliss in the Mirror",
      "effect": "Target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; banish 1 \"Maliss\" monster from your hand or face-up field, and if you do, negate the targeted monster's effects until the end of this turn. If this card is banished: You can target 1 \"Maliss\" card in your GY; banish it, and if you do, add 1 \"Maliss\" card of the same type (Monster, Spell, or Trap) from your Deck to your hand. You can only use each effect of \"Maliss in the Mirror\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
